</div>			
						<h1>Perfect Setup: Ubuntu Hardy+Nginx+MySQL5+PHP5+Wordress</h1>
			
			<div class="date">
				<p>August 16, 2008 by <a href="http://www.mensk.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by admin">admin</a>&nbsp;</p>
			</div>
		
			<style type="text/css">
<!--
